title: Low-Key Script with Key Illustration Hoodie | Minimal Definition Backprint
description:
Soft, quiet confidence you can pull on and go. This cozy hooded sweatshirt settles around you like a calm moment—clean white canvas, delicate black line art, and subtle typography that reads like a private note. A small key motif on each sleeve and a understated ‘low-key’ definition on the back make the design thoughtful, not loud. Wear it to slow mornings with coffee, late-night walks, or when you want your outfit to whisper rather than shout. The roomy pouch and double-lined hood keep things comfortable; the neutral palette layers easily with denim, joggers, or a favorite coat. For someone who prefers understatement and craft over flash, this hoodie feels personal and steady.

Product features
- Soft 50/50 cotton-poly blend for warmth and smooth printability
- Kangaroo pouch pocket to warm hands and carry small items
- Color-matched drawcord and double-lined hood for durability and style
- Tubular knit (no side seams) for a clean look and reduced fabric waste
- DTF/DTG-ready blank with optional embroidery placements on chest and wrists

Care instructions
- Tumble dry: medium
- Iron, steam or dry: low heat
- Do not dryclean
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)
- Non-chlorine: bleach as needed
